{"tid":1984581,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[畢業求幫忙] 反修例運動國際線問卷","createTime":"2020-04-22T14:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T02:03:07.000Z","uid":355266,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"88a4c107357002f448987c916969b45d4345abda","tid":1984581,"uid":355266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"各位手足，唔知可唔可以幫手做份有關反修例運動國際線嘅問卷， master畢業論文用的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去問卷右上角可以揀語言<br />\n<a href=\"http://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_8vHUlSrOfWgRast\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcuhk.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_8vHUlSrOfWgRast&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=73b6147b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_8vHUlSrOfWgRast</a><br />\n<br />\n份paper主要係從社會心理學角度出發，想搵吓有啲乜嘢因素驅使人去參與國際線嘅行動，而「國際線」究竟會唔會對參加者/非參加者有啲咩影響/轉變。得出嚟個result係諗住思考吓「國際線」可以點走落去，如果份嘢寫得正正常常，第時有機會可能share個結果出嚟大家一齊討論吓。<br />\n<br />\n為咗保障各位，份問卷係匿名的，亦set好唔會記錄IP等等任何可以識別到受訪者的個人資料。份問卷全部都係選擇題，除咗問你大概參加過幾多次唔同類型嘅活動之外，唔會問到你參加嘅任何細節，希望可以令大家放心啲。當然，保護自己好緊要，做到一半想唔做，可以隨時退出。<br />\n<br />\n所以如果做完份問卷覺得可以的話，大家都可以推吓同埋share俾身邊親朋好友去做。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以幫幫手，感謝! 如有任何意見，都歡迎留底個comment! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJ圖在此<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/73252838_143052873729749_5436431069106667520_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=2d5d41&amp;_nc_ohc=lw6CasWugfgAX8vxAFg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=bfa8502143dfea180491555b4d434c42&amp;oe=5EC74D08\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F73252838_143052873729749_5436431069106667520_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D2d5d41%26_nc_ohc%3Dlw6CasWugfgAX8vxAFg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3Dbfa8502143dfea180491555b4d434c42%26oe%3D5EC74D08&h=69918e11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b5b540724e962